    "body_html": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-collapse:collapse;caption-side:bottom;background-color: #f2f2f2; margin: 0; padding: 0;\" data-oe-version=\"1.0\">\n  <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n    <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n      <td align=\"center\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;padding: 20px 0;\">\n        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-collapse:collapse;caption-side:bottom;max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #101820; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n          <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n            <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n              <td style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;padding: 20px;\">\n                \n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin: 0; padding: 0; font-size: 13px;\">\n                  Dear <t t-out=\"object.partner_id.name or 'Applicant'\"/>,\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Thank you for your interest in joining the <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or 'Our Company'\"/></b> team. We appreciate the time and effort you put into your application.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Application Review -->\n                  Our hiring team has carefully reviewed your resume and qualifications. While we found your experience to be competitive, we have decided to move forward with other candidates at this time.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Reassurance & Invitation to Connect -->\n                  We understand that recruitment is a complex process, and sometimes great candidates are not selected for specific roles. If you feel we have overlooked something in your application, or if you would like more information about our decision, please do not hesitate to reply to this email.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Future Opportunities -->\n                  We will keep your resume on file and may reach out in the future if an opportunity better aligns with your skills and experience.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  <!-- Closing -->\n                  We sincerely appreciate your interest in our company and wish you the best in your job search. We hope to have the opportunity to connect with you again in the future.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Best regards,<br/>\n                  The HR Team<br/>\n                  <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or 'Our Company'\"/><br/>\n                  <a t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;text-decoration: none; color: #374151;\">\n                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"/>\n                  </a>\n                </p>\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n",
